com.pom.crimson.pages

Class ChangePasswordPage

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.pom.crimson.base.BaseFixture
      • com.pom.crimson.base.BasePage
        • com.pom.crimson.pages.ChangePasswordPage

  • public class ChangePasswordPage
extends BasePage
    This is the Page Class for Change password page in the mobile application.
    User can navigate to this page by going to:

    Profile menu from home page Tab bar
    Clicking on Change password menu from profile menu
    This page class contains MobileElements on this page and functions to simulate interactions with these elements.
    Author:
    Balaji.Sridharan
